         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#FFFFFF"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <categoryValueRef>sid-ddffaa1c-c2c4-4b5f-add4-3a31163e3cbd</categoryValueRef>
      </task>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8B15C1EB-2CA2-4824-B970-69F68D9441BB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Notes:
1. ASN is independent of ABR

2. Visual Inspection is done from perspective of quality check. Quality Check will be outside S/4. Accept/Reject decision will be taken accordingly. In Reject, it will require initiation of return.

3. Transportation is owned by Customer/Support. Factory to Factory transportation (internal to manufacturing operation) is owned by Intel Foundry. Transportation cost will be incorporated by Pricing Team irrespective of customer.

4. UNBW (non-Valuated) will be only for Bailed Material. 

5. Batch lot notification is essentially a 4B2 receipts	


</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E68FF538-5A41-4C6D-B575-63C3BEC073A1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer/freight forwarder will provide declared value of bailed material which will be captured as Statistical Price Condition in S/4 for printing Commercial Invoice.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-97829835-B624-4BAA-B341-6CD3689CDDA2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer/Supplier/OSAT/Forwarding Agents on behalf of customer issue Bailed Material and notify Intel via ASN as soon as material leaves site

</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-ddffaa1c-c2c4-4b5f-add4-3a31163e3cbd" id="sid-DDA9CB34-20D2-4669-915B-AB949F87DBCF">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="center" ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="41.0" y="-12.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
   </process>
